ZH: 我的妈妈一手做的饭非常好吃。
EN: The meal my mom made is very delicious.

ZH: 他一手抓住了从窗户掉下来的小鸟。
EN: He caught the little bird that fell from the window with one hand.

ZH: 她一手牵着孩子，一手提着购物袋。
EN: She held her child with one hand and carried the shopping bags with the other.

ZH: 他是一手打造了这家公司的成功。
EN: He is the one who built the success of this company.

ZH: 她是这个项目的一手策划者。
EN: She is the mastermind behind this project.

ZH: 我家的电视、冰箱、洗衣机都是他一手选购的。
EN: He personally selected all the television, refrigerator, and washing machine in our house.

